Author: little-pinkie
Text: I’ve had them before. 2 weeks ago I was really shook up and wasn’t sure what was happening or what was wrong. I always question myself while it’s happening. I push through it and take an anxiety pill (hydroxyzine/Benadryl/Ativan) and try to sleep as much as I can. It’s lasted days before for me. I try to eat just the right amount and do the bare minimum of self care. It’s hard but it’s okay to ask for help.
